flowchart TD
    A[Want to Use OBS with TikTok Live Studio] --> B{TikTok Live Studio Virtual Camera Status}
    B -->|Locked| C[Error: Unlock Virtual Camera]
    B -->|Unlocked| D[Can Use OBS Virtual Camera]
    
    C --> E[Requirement: Go Live 3 Times for 25 Minutes Each]
    E --> F{Physical Camera Available?}
    
    F -->|Yes - Built-in Camera| G[Use Built-in Camera]
    F -->|Yes - USB Webcam| H[Use USB Webcam]
    F -->|No| I[Buy Cheap USB Webcam]
    
    G --> J{Camera Recognized as Physical?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Go Live 3 Times]
    J -->|No - Detected as Virtual| L[Update Camera Drivers or Use USB Webcam]
    
    H --> K
    I --> K
    L --> K
    
    K --> M[Wait Up to 48 Hours for Validation]
    M --> N{Virtual Camera Unlocked?}
    
    N -->|Yes| D
    N -->|No| O[Check TikTok Account Status or Contact Support]
    
    D --> P[Set Up OBS Scene with Overlays]
    P --> Q[Add Browser Sources: TikFinity/StreamElements]
    Q --> R[Start OBS Virtual Camera]
    R --> S[Add OBS Virtual Camera to TikTok Live Studio]
    S --> T[Go Live with Overlays]
    
    style A fill:#e1f5ff
